sub_title: Quality & Safety Coordinator / Aerospace Lead Auditor /  Director - 9100, 9110, 9120 AEA
summary:
Experienced Aerospace engineer, auditor, project manager
AEA (Aerospace Industry Auditor) AS/EN9100, 9110, 9120
ISO17025:2017 Lead Auditor

Specialities :
- AS9100D,AS9110C, AS9120B, FAA AC 00-56, ISO17025:2017 third party/certification audits, second party/supplier audits, internal audits, internal auditor trainings, awareness trainings, implementation consultancy.
- SAR / EASA / CASA part 145, SMS internal audits, second party/supplier audits, implementation consultancy
- aircraft maintenance start to end internal audits, clients complaints investigations
- outsourced aerospace quality & safety management (part time contract work)
- ATA Spec 300 trainings
- aerospace engineering, project management & quality management instructor
